    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels that still has some good use left in it? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, runs, and can be a great fit for someone who wants affordable transportation, a project, or a handy backup vehicle. I\u2019m listing it honestly and keeping the price realistic\u2014if you want something budget-friendly without any fluff, this is worth a look. Happy to answer questions and help you see if it\u2019s the right fit.",
      "price": 5900.0,
