      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project or budget driver with a strong mechanical feel and plenty of usable life for the right owner. The powertrain pulls through the rev range, the chassis is straightforward, and it has the kind of simple, serviceable setup that makes it appealing for someone who knows their way around basic upkeep. Cosmetically it shows wear and needs attention in spots, but it presents as an honest vehicle with good bones, a practical layout, and real potential as a dependable runabout, weekend fixer, or parts-friendly platform. Priced to move for someone looking for capability over cosmetics.",
      "price": 5900.0,
